content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 335.16 - Service not credited

State Regulations

As defined in this Part, service in academic rank shall
not be credited as eligible service for permanent appointment. As defined in
this Part, service in professional title shall not be credited as eligible
service for continuing appointment. Notes
